task.summary: feat : migrated from dagger 2.0 to hilt

feat : implemented cat list maintaining corner cases using pagging library, mvvm, live data and Rx
#Feature 1 ...................... # Load the cat images from ​api.thecatapi.com, ​limit each page to 20 images e.g https://api.thecatapi.com/v1/images/search?limit=20&page=1&mime_types=png # Display the cat images in a ​square-3 column​ layout while maintaining the aspect ratio of the image # Allow the user to browse and scroll through the endless cat images
feat : implemented onlick event on each item and image full screen view

feat : resize image keeping while maintaining the aspect ratio of the image
# Display the cat images in a ​square-3 column​ layout while maintaining the aspect ratio of the image

feat : migration from 'android.arch.paging:runtime:1.0.0' to "androidx.paging:paging-runtime:3.0.0-alpha03", implemented primary base of database for offliner support..
# Migrated to jetpack paging 3.0.0 for better performance on scrolling, loading and control on development part
# Created Loading adapter (footer) for inserting loading
# Created database primary base classes

feat : primary implementation on offline support using madiator and local database
# keys will be coming nul if we use paging version above 3.0.0-alpha02

feat : offline support compelete
# Support offline-first architecture for low-speed connections optimization and offline capabilities by storing data in local database

feat : pinch to zoom implemented
# [Bonus] ​Add-on pinch-to-zoom feature, similar but not strictly necessary to be the same with ​sample.mov

feat : Project Setup
####################### Supported Android versions: Android 21+ Supported densities: hdpi, xhdpi and xxhdpi Tablets support: not required Supported language: English Package: com.sevenpeakssoftware.xxx (use your name instead of xxx)
